---
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-label">About</div>
      <h2>Perspective-first<br/><span class="grad-text">engineering.</span></h2>
      <p>저는 <strong>Bigtablet, Inc.의 프론트엔드 개발자</strong>로,
         여러 운영 환경에서 마주치는 문제를 하나씩 해결하며 경험을 쌓고 있습니다.</p>
      <p>프로덕션에서는 <strong>BFF 보안 아키텍처</strong>와 FIDO2 패스키 인증을 구현하고,
         여러 프로덕트에서 사용하는 디자인 시스템과 웹 성능 개선 작업에 참여했습니다.</p>
      <p>업무 밖에서는 Rust 학습 가이드와 작은 도구를 만들며,
         관심 있는 기술을 직접 구현하고 이해하는 과정을 즐깁니다.</p>
      <blockquote class="philosophy">
        <span>"사용자의 관점으로 바라보기"</span><br/>
        모든 기술적 결정은 결국 UX 결정입니다.
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-grid reveal d2">
      <div class="stat-card c1">
        <div class="num">BFF</div>
        <div class="lbl">Security Pattern</div>
        <div class="sub">HttpOnly JWT · URL 차단</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card c2">
        <div class="num" data-count="100" data-suffix="%">100%</div>
        <div class="lbl">Test Coverage</div>
        <div class="sub">BFF + 유틸 레이어</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card c3">
        <div class="num" data-count="93" data-suffix="%">93%</div>
        <div class="lbl">LCP 개선율</div>
        <div class="sub">5.22s → 0.36s</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card c4">
        <div class="num" data-count="5" data-suffix="+">5+</div>
        <div class="lbl">Products</div>
        <div class="sub">디자인 시스템 사용 중</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../styles/tokens' as *;

  #about { padding: clamp(5rem,10vw,9rem) clamp(1.5rem,5vw,4rem); }

  .about-grid {
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start;
  }

  h2 { font-family:$font-display; font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.2rem); font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-.03em; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
  p  { font-size:1rem; color:$text-secondary; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:1.15rem; strong{color:$text-primary;font-weight:600;} }

  .philosophy {
    margin-top:1.5rem; padding:1.2rem 1.5rem; background:$bg-elevated;
    border-left:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:0 $r-md $r-md 0;
    font-style:italic; color:$text-secondary; font-size:.9rem; line-height:1.65;
    span{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);font-weight:500;font-style:normal;}
  }

  .stats-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1rem; }
  .stat-card {
    padding:1.4rem 1.5rem; background:$bg-elevated; border:1px solid $border;
    border-radius:$r-lg; transition:border-color $mid, transform $mid; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
    &::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,transparent 60%,rgba(255,255,255,.025));opacity:0;transition:opacity $mid;}
    &:hover{border-color:$border-hover;transform:translateY(-3px);}
    &:hover::before{opacity:1;}
    .num{font-family:$font-display;font-size:2.1rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.04em;line-height:1;margin-bottom:.35rem;color:#ffffff;}
    .lbl{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:$text-muted;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;}
    .sub{font-size:.72rem;color:$text-muted;margin-top:.2rem;}
    &.c1 .num{opacity:1;} &.c2 .num{opacity:.85;} &.c3 .num{opacity:.7;} &.c4 .num{opacity:.6;}
  }

  @media(max-width:900px){.about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:3rem;}.stats-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);}}
  @media(max-width:640px){.stats-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}}
</style>
